  ('optometrist-moex-01810', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-109-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '患者戴-5.00 DS眼鏡時，可看清眼前67公分至100公分。欲看清楚眼前33公分至40公分影像，眼鏡需 為多少屈光度？', '["-2.50DS", "-3.00DS", "-3.50DS", "-4.00DS"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce0dc77563b8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a1c83f3335a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-01811', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-109-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有一孩童在未使用鏡片矯治下，發現物體移近至眼前 33 公分時變模糊。雙眼未散瞳前+2.00 DS，經睫狀 肌麻痺後，發現雙眼為+6.00DS。他的調節幅度（amplitudeofaccommodation）應為多少？', '["5.00D", "6.00D", "8.00D", "9.00D"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce0dc77563b8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a1c83f3335a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 42, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-01812', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-109-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '何先生一位-8.00 D近視的病人，當他戴上可完全矯正他度數的隱形眼鏡時，有一個200公分的超焦距離 （hyperfocaldistance）。如果他的調節近點（nearpointofaccommodation）為20公分，他的真正調節幅度 （trueamplitudeofaccommodation）為多少？', '["1.00D", "4.00D", "4.50D", "5.50D"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce0dc77563b8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a1c83f3335a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 43, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
